13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 3, Chapter 22, 2nd
15 Extraordinary Session, O.S.L. 2022, as amended by Section 1, Chapter
16 437, O.S.L. 2024 (62 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 255.4), is amended to
17 read as follows:
18 Section 255.4. A. There is hereby created in the State
19 Treasury a revolving fund for the Oklahoma Department of Commerce
20 Workforce Commission to be designated the “Workforce Coordination
21 Revolving Fund”. The fund shall be a continuing fund, not subject
22 to fiscal year limitations, and shall consist of all monies directed
23 for deposit by law.
